title: [A Flash Of Strength, Reception]
description: Large windows draped with faded cotton allow muted moonlight to breach the dim receiving room.  A worn oak table and benches sit before an old stone fireplace, hot coals glowing from within the firebox.  Thick, dirty rushes mixed with bits of dried food and drink cover the scarred wooden floor.
